data.description: Custom built home on a 1 acre lot in The Hills of Argyle! This gorgeous property features 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, an office, formal dining room, bonus room, theater room, updated kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a breakfast nook looking out to the pool area. The backyard is an outdoor resort oasis with a saltwater pool, spa, river rock landscaping, flagstone patio, outdoor kitchen with sunk in cooler and a built in refrigerator. This home is part of the highly rated Argyle ISD.
